data.description: Don't miss this turnkey two story Condo! This property has 1253 Square feet which includes 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, an attached 2 car garage and a private upgraded backyard with pavers and artificial grass. All appliances included with a brand new refrigerator.  The HOA includes many great amenities. Open floor design with pantry and breakfast bar. Don't pass up this beauty!
